Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达孜 X-Rounder们的冰眠结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是今天吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 据报刚才已经全部苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔哥哥 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 德西尔哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜伏任务归来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听闻您的冰眠结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特此赶来报告哥哥一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 潜伏任务一定够呛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样高水平的X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小享有高度自由的权限 活跃在前线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不会像你这样被派去杂用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而还会受到保护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特看人从不走眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特司令官 可以进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令官 各部队作战准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被任命为地球占领军司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时哥哥在冰眠中…故未能及时报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令官 你爬到我的头上去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预计抵达作战宇域前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体将会调试完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要和我说预计
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次作战意义重大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断进化的机动战士 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构成其中枢的AGE系统 就是我们的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据情报 AGE系统的核心部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就置于高达胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战场上随时收集需要的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即是说 这次的目标是AGE系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取也好 破坏也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样 难免与高达一战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 竟然有这样的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方的技术水准完全出乎我们预料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦至今未能解密AGE系统的内部程序
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以至于无法拷贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只要控制它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以阻止高达进一步进化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是高达母舰的预测航线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们中途埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 如果去往联邦总司令部巨环基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最短的路径…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,XD37 岩礁宇域…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号 即将驶入XD37岩礁宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员进入多障碍区域航行态势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么那么没骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想 索敌系统的性能发挥会受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才能不被维甘发现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是变更航线的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下要尽可能避免战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗…能避开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽 在想什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是在担心那家伙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不！ 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 新兵蛋子 吃得惯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是嚼完了咽下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让它变成打仗时的力气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和正常吃有什么区别？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么区别 有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照做就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能吃的时候使劲吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别等饿了后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 敌人什么时候来都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调试已经全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会让我满意吗 杰德拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰德拉是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为发挥X-Rounder实力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专门研发的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击时请记得戴上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是控制杰哈特大人X-Rounder能力的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更准确的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有助于能力的稳定发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和机体实现沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就杰哈特大人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果最大限度发挥能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体本身会支撑不住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有力量的不便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短时间内反复佩卸无法发挥其性能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长期征战时请平日就戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 红得就像个靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看 司令官大人的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在说服不了自己和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你愁眉苦脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么话跟我说吧 不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次出战的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有想过敌人机师的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？没那种闲工夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有工夫也不会去想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人屁股就是被用来打的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们家的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员战斗配置 全员战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始对照索敌数据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各应急班站点就位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会在这条路径上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埋伏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸 保养完了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是老爸 是爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 要叫我中尉 说了多少遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了 保养完没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…没问题 亚瑟姆的AGE-2也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克中尉你真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唠唠叨叨又要被妈妈说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克先生是你爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都说我像妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统对照完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多拉多 6机 巴库多 2机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏在这种地方进入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 新兵蛋子们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩礁宇域的战斗 对你们来说还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 敌人来了就没有不迎接的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别因为上次的事畏畏缩缩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻就该有点冲劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走 沃尔夫队出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆·明日野 高达AGE-2 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫队 出击完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对维甘机动战士部队 采取迎击态势…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B543反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌机后方又出现疑似维甘机体1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在以三倍速度接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 你是我的对手吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌机后方B543 出现疑似维甘机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向沃尔夫队接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他机体的三倍速度？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么来头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩礁宇域里这种速度？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 保佑我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小的们 客人不是只有一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先试试手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也行 就像上次那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一架架来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇静 镇静 镇静 镇静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明机种 闯入机动战士队战斗宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 我来会会你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是我一厢情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 先打下一架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 它奔你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台机体能跟上我的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种程度吗 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是新型机的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃得也挺快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来晚了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特 麦克斯 阿莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂兵交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不是杂兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎 我们俩一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 一对一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的对手是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一台在攻击高达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他根本不做理睬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看破了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特！ 是杰哈特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 是杰哈特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是对手又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫我是又如何 为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想战斗的话 就从战场上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连撤退的觉悟也没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来此的目的就是击落高达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你当作朋友 是我的一厢情愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊 杰哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是 这么好欺负的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种程度就敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我面前撒野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来就来 给你个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有冲劲是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了什么都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 X-Rounder的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之所以不适合战斗 不只是因为天真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说 司令官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让高达给逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹩脚的谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放水饶了朋友一命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想骗过我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果伊泽尔坎特大人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己关在房间里 看来该教训下他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:21:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人 有时候会需要一个人静下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特 是故意放过我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想说 我没有上战场的实力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Rounder…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也！
